window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>In this interactive study, biblical counselor John Henderson uses a workbook approach to guide you through your marriage preparation - helping you to understand the purpose of marriage, to handle conflict, to glorify Christ in your union and finances, and to get to know your own heart and expectations. Many threats to a marriage can be identified even before the wedding takes place. Even better, God's gospel provides the means of overcoming them.</p>"; 
